可解释性 (Mechanistic Interpretability)",{"type":181,"children":182,"toc":371},"root",[183,191,198,204,235,241,246,273,279,284,311,317,322,341,347,352],{"type":184,"tag":185,"props":186,"children":188},"element","h1",{"id":187},"机制可解释性-mechanistic-interpretability",[189],{"type":190,"value":179},"text",{"type":184,"tag":192,"props":193,"children":195},"h2",{"id":194},"transformerlens逆向工程-gpt-风格模型的标准工具",[196],{"type":190,"value":197},"TransformerLens：逆向工程 GPT 风格模型的标准工具",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":200,"children":201},"p",{},[202],{"type":190,"value":203},"TransformerLens 由 Neel Nanda 开发，是机制可解释性领域的事实标准工具。它提供对 GPT 风格语言模型内部的深度访问能力，包括激活缓存、注意力模式分析、因果追踪和激活修补（Activation Patching）。使用它可以重现经典研究：归纳头（Induction Heads）负责 few-shot 学习的注意力回路、间接对象识别（IOI）解析代词指代消解的电路、以及定位执行简单数学运算的子网络。",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":205,"children":206},{},[207,209,218,220,227,228],{"type":190,"value":208},"见：",{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":211,"children":215},"a",{"href":212,"rel":213},"https://github.com/TransformerLensOrg/TransformerLens",[214],"nofollow",[216],{"type":190,"value":217},"TransformerLens GitHub",{"type":190,"value":219}," | ",{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":221,"children":224},{"href":222,"rel":223},"https://neelnanda-io.github.io/TransformerLens/",[214],[225],{"type":190,"value":226},"TransformerLens 教程",{"type":190,"value":219},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":229,"children":232},{"href":230,"rel":231},"https://arxiv.org/html/2404.15255v1",[214],[233],{"type":190,"value":234},"Activation Patching 论文",{"type":184,"tag":192,"props":236,"children":238},{"id":237},"稀疏自动编码器将神经元分解为可解释特征",[239],{"type":190,"value":240},"稀疏自动编码器：将神经元分解为可解释特征",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":242,"children":243},{},[244],{"type":190,"value":245},"稀疏自动编码器（SAE）是当前可解释性研究的热点方向。它将高维激活向量分解为稀疏的、可解释的\"特征\"基向量，这些特征往往对应人类可理解的概念：数字、颜色、语法结构、甚至抽象的情感概念。Anthropic 在 Claude 3 Sonnet 上的研究发现，约 70% 的 SAE 特征可被人类解释，实现了从\"多义神经元\"到\"单语义特征\"的突破。",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":247,"children":248},{},[249,250,257,258,265,266],{"type":190,"value":208},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":251,"children":254},{"href":252,"rel":253},"https://transformer-circuits.pub/2024/scaling-monosemanticity/",[214],[255],{"type":190,"value":256},"Anthropic SAE 研究",{"type":190,"value":219},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":259,"children":262},{"href":260,"rel":261},"https://nickjiang.substack.com/p/a-primer-on-sparse-autoencoders",[214],[263],{"type":190,"value":264},"SAE 入门指南",{"type":190,"value":219},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":267,"children":270},{"href":268,"rel":269},"https://github.com/jbloomAus/SAELens",[214],[271],{"type":190,"value":272},"SAELens GitHub",{"type":184,"tag":192,"props":274,"children":276},{"id":275},"nnsight-与-ndif远程可解释性实验基础设施",[277],{"type":190,"value":278},"nnsight 与 NDIF：远程可解释性实验基础设施",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":280,"children":281},{},[282],{"type":190,"value":283},"传统可解释性工具受限于单机 GPU 显存，难以分析 70B+ 参数模型。nnsight 通过远程执行架构解决了这个问题——本地编写干预逻辑，远程在大型 GPU 集群执行，只返回分析结果。National Deep Inference Facility (NDIF) 为研究者提供免费的远程可解释性计算资源，让任何研究者都能分析 Llama-2-70B 级别的模型。",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":285,"children":286},{},[287,288,295,296,303,304],{"type":190,"value":208},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":289,"children":292},{"href":290,"rel":291},"https://nnsight.net/",[214],[293],{"type":190,"value":294},"nnsight 文档",{"type":190,"value":219},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":297,"children":300},{"href":298,"rel":299},"https://github.com/ndif-team/nnsight",[214],[301],{"type":190,"value":302},"nnsight GitHub",{"type":190,"value":219},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":305,"children":308},{"href":306,"rel":307},"https://ndif.us/",[214],[309],{"type":190,"value":310},"NDIF 官网",{"type":184,"tag":192,"props":312,"children":314},{"id":313},"归纳头few-shot-学习的注意力回路",[315],{"type":190,"value":316},"归纳头：Few-shot 学习的注意力回路",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":318,"children":319},{},[320],{"type":190,"value":321},"归纳头是 Transformer 中一种特殊的注意力头模式，负责识别序列中的重复模式并进行 few-shot 学习。当一个 token 在序列中重复出现时，归纳头能够\"复制\"之前出现的模式，这是大模型上下文学习能力的重要机制。通过 TransformerLens 的激活修补技术，可以精确定位这些回路并研究其工作机制。",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":323,"children":324},{},[325,326,333,334],{"type":190,"value":208},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":327,"children":330},{"href":328,"rel":329},"https://aclanthology.org/2025.acl-long.442.pdf",[214],[331],{"type":190,"value":332},"Circuit Stability 论文",{"type":190,"value":219},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":335,"children":338},{"href":336,"rel":337},"https://www.alignmentforum.org/posts/jP9KDyMkchuv6tHwm/how-to-become-a-mechanistic-interpretability-researcher",[214],[339],{"type":190,"value":340},"如何成为可解释性研究员",{"type":184,"tag":192,"props":342,"children":344},{"id":343},"表征工程主动修改模型内部行为",[345],{"type":190,"value":346},"表征工程：主动修改模型内部行为",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":348,"children":349},{},[350],{"type":190,"value":351},"表征工程（Representation Engineering）是通过定位和修改模型内部表征来实现特定行为的技术。包括增强诚实性（检测并抑制模型幻觉）、提升有用性（增强指令遵循能力）、以及改善安全性（抑制有害输出）。这为 AI 对齐提供了一条不同于 RLHF 的技术路径——直接操作模型的内部表征而非仅仅调整输出分布。",{"type":184,"tag":199,"props":353,"children":354},{},[355,356,363,364],{"type":190,"value":208},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":357,"children":360},{"href":358,"rel":359},"https://www.anthropic.com/research/transformer-circuits",[214],[361],{"type":190,"value":362},"Anthropic 可解释性研究",{"type":190,"value":219},{"type":184,"tag":210,"props":365,"children":368},{"href":366,"rel":367},"https://arena-chapter1-transformer-interp.streamlit.app/",[214],[369],{"type":190,"value":370},"ARENA 可解释性教程",{"title":178,"searchDepth":372,"depth":372,"links":373},2,[374,375,376,377,378],{"id":194,"depth":372,"text":197},{"id":237,"depth":372,"text":240},{"id":275,"depth":372,"text":278},{"id":313,"depth":372,"text":316},{"id":343,"depth":372,"text":346},"markdown","content:6.maps:_ai:mechanistic-interpretability.md","content","6.maps/_ai/mechanistic-interpretability.md","6.maps/_ai/mechanistic-interpretability","md",[386,390],{"_path":387,"title":388,"description":389},"/maps/_ai/mcp/native-api-to-mcp","反对「直接把内部 API 暴露成 MCP」的天真做法","原文反对将现有内部 API 直接转换为 MCP，建议为代理场景专门设计安全的 MCP 服务层。",{"_path":391,"title":392,"description":178},"/maps/_ai/mlops","MLOps",1771695830050]